content: If you want help and consultations, this free show celebrated a bunch of queer Brazilian celebrities and had some Easter eggs (like a vip area for people with Madonna tattoos). I wasn’t there in person but I’m a translator and also have friends who have gone there (and into the vip) if u ever wanna talk about the amazing things this show covered and celebrated I’ve been a big supporter of ur channel for years and work in translation would love to help as I can, offer some clips for a special clip breakdown or something. Come back soon we have plenty of cool states around here.
